 is distinguished as   Matthias .  A related name from the same Hebrew roots, but reversed, is   Jonathan .  Throughout the English-speaking world <i>Matthew</i> has been particularly popular since the 1970s."],"variants":[{"name":"Mathew","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Matthew ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Matthew Horbury was born about 1105, in Horbury, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Matthew Horbury about 1125, in Horbury, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1215, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 111."},"et":{"ABT 1105–1215":"umbes 1105–1215","1100–1210":"1100–1210","1130–1196":"1130–1196","1105–1215":"1105–1215","1215":"1215","1105":"1105","1210":"1210","1100":"1100","ABT 1125":"umbes 1125","ABT 1105":"umbes 1105","1130":"1130","1196":"1196","Horbury, Yorkshire, England":"Horbury, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Horbury, Wakefield, Yorkshire, England":"Horbury, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"ABT 1105–1215":"noin 1105–1215","1100–1210":"1100–1210","1130–1196":"1130–1196","1105–1215":"1105–1215","1215":"1215","1105":"1105","1210":"1210","1100":"1100","ABT 1125":"noin 1125","ABT 1105":"noin 1105","1130":"1130","1196":"1196","Horbury, Yorkshire, England":"Horbury, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Horbury, Wakefield, Yorkshire, England":"Horbury, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"ABT 1105–1215":"environ 1105–1215","1100–1210":"1100–1210","1130–1196":"1130–1196","1105–1215":"1105–1215","1215":"1215","1105":"1105","1210":"1210","1100":"1100","ABT 1125":"environ 1125","ABT 1105":"environ 1105","1130":"1130","1196":"1196","Horbury, Yorkshire, England":"Horbury, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Horbury, Wakefield, Yorkshire, England":"Horbury, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Matthew Horbury est